OL,3,CRoyal College of Nursing members vote
OL,4,Cto reject pay offer
OL,6,FMembers of the Royal College of
OL,7,FNursing in Northern Ireland have voted
OL,8,Fto reject a pay offer, while a number
OL,9,Fof other health worker unions have
OL,10,Fvoted to accept it.
OL,12,FIt comes after industrial action over
OL,13,Fpay levels falling behind colleagues
OL,14,Facross the rest of the UK.
OL,16,FFollowing the restoration of devolved
OL,17,Fgovernment at Stormont earlier this
OL,18,Fyear, health workers were offered a 5%
OL,19,Fincrease and a lump sum of #1,505.
