OL,3,CRoyal College of Nursing members vote
OL,4,Cto reject pay offer
OL,6,FRita Devlin, director of the Royal
OL,7,FCollege of Nursing (RCN) in Northern
OL,8,FIreland, said RCN members voted by
OL,9,F55.85% to 44.15% to reject the pay
OL,10,Foffer.
OL,12,FHealth Minister Robin Swann has been
OL,13,Fadvised of the outcome.
OL,15,FMs Devlin said the offer "fell short
OL,16,Fof pay parity with colleagues in
OL,17,FEngland", adding "our members in
OL,18,FNorthern Ireland will not tolerate
OL,19,Fbeing treated unequally and unfairly".
