OL,3,CRoyal College of Nursing members vote
OL,4,Cto reject pay offer
OL,6,F"The RCN remains in dispute and the
OL,7,FRCN Northern Ireland Board, which is
OL,8,Felected by our members, will be
OL,9,Fmeeting as a matter of urgency to
OL,10,Fconsider the results of our ballot and
OL,11,Fto determine the next steps," she said.
OL,13,FMeanwhile other health worker unions
OL,14,Fhave voted to accept a pay offer.
OL,16,FUnison said 29,000 members voted by
OL,17,F77.2% to 22.8%, and Unite said 81% of
OL,18,Ftheir members voted to accept.
