OL,3,CRoyal College of Nursing members vote
OL,4,Cto reject pay offer
OL,6,FMembers of the Royal College of
OL,7,FMidwives also voted to accept with
OL,8,F86.3% voting for, members of the
OL,9,FChartered Society of Physiotherapists
OL,10,Fvoted (84%) to accept as well as the
OL,11,FSociety of Radiographers (73%).
OL,13,FIn a statement, Health Minister Robin
OL,14,FSwann and his department welcomed the
OL,15,F"decisive outcome of trade union
OL,16,Fballots on the pay offer tabled in
OL,17,FFebruary".
OL,19,F"The Department will now move to
OL,20,Fimplement the offer," they said.
