OL,3,CRoyal College of Nursing members vote
OL,4,Cto reject pay offer
OL,6,F"This settlement will restore pay
OL,7,Fparity with England for all health and
OL,8,Fsocial care staff covered by the
OL,9,FAgenda for Change framework.
OL,11,F"Under this package, HSC Agenda for
OL,12,FChange staff will receive a
OL,13,Fconsolidated pay uplift of 5% and a
OL,14,Fnon-consolidated (pro-rata) payment of
OL,15,F#1,505.
OL,17,F"The pay settlement is for the
OL,18,Ffinancial year 2023/24 and will be
OL,19,Fbackdated to April 2023."
